name: Gogogo Aristera & Dexia
desc:
While another "Gogogo" monster is on the field, monsters your opponent controls cannot target face-up "Gogogo" monsters for attacks, also your opponent cannot target face-up "Gogogo" monsters with card effects. An Xyz Monster that was Summoned using only this card and other "Gogogo" monsters as Xyz Material gains this effect.
‚óè When it is Xyz Summoned: You can target 1 face-up Attack Position monster your opponent controls; change it to Defense Position, and if you do, its DEF becomes 0.
